instruction:
Write a story prompt in English suitable for use with an AI that crafts narratives such as comics, fairy tales, or adventure stories. The story should be long enough to provide a minimum reading duration of 5 minutes. Ensure the following requirements are met:

1. Title: Include a relevant, engaging title that fits the theme and tone of the story.
2. Characters: List all main characters, including their names and a brief description of their personalities and roles.
3. Structure: Divide the story into clear, readable sections for better narrative flow.
4. Format: Output the result in plain JSON (without markdown or code blocks), using the following structure:

{
  "title": "Your story title",
  "characters": [
    {
      "name": "Character Name",
      "nature": "Brief description of character's personality and role"
    }
  ],
  "story": [
    {
      "content": "Narrative text for this part of the story",
      "image_prompt": "Short prompt for generating an image based on this section"
    }
  ]
}

Do not wrap the output in ```json or any other markdown formatting.
